href="http://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0147097">
CHSalign: a web server that builds upon Junction-Explorer and RNAJAG for
pairwise alignment of RNA secondary structures with coaxial helical
stacking</a>.
<I>PLoS One</I> 2016;11(1):e0147097.<br>
